The bottle is, by far, the coolest packaging I have seen. It came in a nifty box, like an old-school apothecary arriving with the elixir of life, or health, or something like that. Cool, cool, cool... It is 1 TBSP to 8 oz. of water/milk. Here is what I found - I think 8 oz water and another oz or so of cream/creamer is about right. It is just a bit bitter still, but certainly enjoyable. There are other options in the "coffee concentrate" aisle that I might like a bit better, but this is a good price point, so...

product_name: Jot Concentrated Coffee - 20X Stronger Than Regular Coffee or Cold Brew - 150 mg of Caffeine - Create Instant Iced Coffee or Add a Shot for a Latte - 1 Bottle (14 Servings)
review_content: I mix a tablespoon of Jot, a tablespoon of Starbucks caramel syrup and whole milk and add ice!  Makes the most delicious drink!

product_name: Javy Coffee Microdose 30X Liquid Coffee Concentrate, Artisan Roasted Cold Brew Coffee Arabica, Unsweetened Iced Coffee & Cold-Brew, Concentrated Cold Brew Coffee, Ice Coffee 6oz. Bottle, 30 Servings
review_content: I spend way too much money on coffee and this is about to save me some money. This is so delicious. The flavor is great. I’m more of a hot coffee gal so I did it with hot water and my roommate did it with cold. We both love it and will definitely order more

product_name: Javy Coffee Microdose 30X Liquid Coffee Concentrate, Artisan Roasted Cold Brew Coffee Arabica, Unsweetened Iced Coffee & Cold-Brew, Concentrated Cold Brew Coffee, Ice Coffee 6oz. Bottle, 30 Servings
review_content: Ok this is so good and easy. I work in the OR and this makes me grabbing a coffee so easy. I filled a cup with water and poured in some Javy and mixed with a protein shake. No more spending $3-6 on a coffee in the cafeteria. At home i usually make my iced coffee with the starbucks cold brew and this is BETTER. The taste is so good! Will definitely be using this from now on, even at home! Would recommend to everyone!

product_name: Javy Coffee Microdose 30X Liquid Coffee Concentrate, Artisan Roasted Cold Brew Coffee Arabica, Unsweetened Iced Coffee & Cold-Brew, Concentrated Cold Brew Coffee, Ice Coffee 6oz. Bottle, 30 Servings
review_content: I was pleasantly suprised by how smooth the coffee tastes. So far ive made it w Almond milk and water, both times were just as good. No regrets on this purchase!

product_name: Jot Concentrated Coffee - 20X Stronger Than Regular Coffee or Cold Brew - 150 mg of Caffeine - Create Instant Iced Coffee or Add a Shot for a Latte - 1 Bottle (14 Servings)
review_content: Finding that perfect balance of concentrate to other liquid is still a process.  Too much, and it's bitter.  Too little, and there isn't enough flavor.  All-in-all though, I like it.

product_name: Jot Concentrated Coffee - 20X Stronger Than Regular Coffee or Cold Brew - 150 mg of Caffeine - Create Instant Iced Coffee or Add a Shot for a Latte - 1 Bottle (14 Servings)
review_content: For the size coffee mug I use, two teaspoons works perfect! Awesome flavor. If it's bitter, you may be using too much Jot for the water you're using.
